== 改編電視劇 ==
2012年10月，[[福斯廣播公司|福斯廣播公司]]宣布，有意將《[[戰地風雲：惡名昭彰|戰地風雲：惡名昭彰]]》改編成約一小時的電視劇。該劇由執行製片人{{link-en|約翰·艾森德斯|John Eisendrath}}與派翠克·巴赫編劇，而美商藝電的派翠克·奧布萊恩與[[快樂麥迪遜|快樂麥迪遜]]的道格·羅賓森則共同擔任監製<ref>{{cite web| last = Andreeva| first = Nellie| title = Fox To Develop Action TV Series Based On Video Game 'Battlefield: Bad Company'| work = [[Deadline.com|Deadline]]| publisher = [[PMC_(company)|PMC (company)]]| date = October 8, 2012| url = http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/battlefield-bad-company-tv-series-fox-electronic-arts-alias/| accessdate = October 8, 2012| archive-date = 2014-07-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140729193717/http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/battlefield-bad-company-tv-series-fox-electronic-arts-alias/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2016年7月，{{link-en|派拉蒙電視公司|Paramount Television}}宣布，打算將該遊戲系列改編成電視劇。{{link-en|Anonymous Content|Anonymous Content}}的麥可·休格和艾許利·扎爾塔將擔任執行製片人<ref>{{cite web| url=http://deadline.com/2016/07/battlefield-video-game-tv-series-paramount-tv-michael-sugar-1201784860/| last=Petski| first=Denise| title=‘Battlefield’ Video Game To Be Adapted As TV Series By Paramount TV & Anonymous Content| date=July 11, 2016| accessdate=July 11, 2016| archive-date=2021-01-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117164601/https://deadline.com/2016/07/battlefield-video-game-tv-series-paramount-tv-michael-sugar-1201784860/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

